message.title: GIP-21: Amendment to GIP-17. Send additional funds to daughter Safe
message.body:
Should GnosisDAO implement GIP-21 as detailed in this forum post?

https://forum.gnosis.io/t/gip-21-amendment-to-gip-17-send-additional-funds-to-daughter-safe/2699

Transactions in this proposal:
- Send tokens to Daughter Safe
